    "The reliability of SDs is difficult to determine as there are no evaluation metrics so far since this aspect of AI is still under development.",
    "One possible way to determine the robustness of SDs is to involve subject-level experts such as doctors for medical images, to validate the accuracy of the images before utilization and is an area of future research.",
    "Es, GANs and diffusion models have been utilized in healthcare research to generate SDs.",
    "Synthetic data customized to the need of researchers can be produced to train robust AI models.",
    "These models, having been trained on such a diverse dataset will be applicable for dissemination across countries."
